I understand.

18
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:09,667
I think for you,

19
00:01:09,833 --> 00:01:12,767
Kin-chan suits better than Irie.
To be honest.

20
00:01:12,933 --> 00:01:15,200
-Satomi.
-Think about it.

21
00:01:15,367 --> 00:01:18,900
Irie has been suggestive to you

22
00:01:19,067 --> 00:01:20,700
and he even kissed you.

23
