with a different girl easily.

24
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:26,267
Being your best friend,
I can't forgive him.

25
00:01:26,433 --> 00:01:28,167
Right. During all that,

26
00:01:28,333 --> 00:01:29,867
Kin-chan has been

27
00:01:30,033 --> 00:01:32,800
in love with only Kotoko
the whole time.

28
00:01:32,900 --> 00:01:35,733
You've said that

29
