that you don't have,

33
00:01:45,167 --> 00:01:48,400
but the person you can stay
together with longer,

34
00:01:48,567 --> 00:01:51,533
the person who makes you happy
for the rest of your life,

35
00:01:51,700 --> 00:01:53,567
is a guy like Kin-chan.

36
00:01:53,733 --> 00:01:55,633
That's what I think.

37
00:01:55,800 --> 00:02:00,400
It makes women happier
to be loved than to love.

38
00:02:00,567 --> 00:02:02,600
Take this chance

39
00:02:02,767 --> 00:02:05,100
to consider Kin-chan seriously.

40
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:18,667
Here's the sake for you.

41
00:02:18,833 --> 00:02:20,400
All right.

42
00:02:20,567 --> 00:02:21,967
You're cheerful as always.

43
00:02:22,133 --> 00:02:24,033
Thank you.

44
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:26,233
I wish a cheerful guy like you

45
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,433
were in my restaurant.

46
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,800
-No, no.
-I own

47
00:02:30,967 --> 00:02:32,067
a Japanese restaurant.

48
00:02:32,233 --> 00:02:34,767
-Where?
-I'm not telling you.

49
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,167
-Tell me.
-Do you want to know?

50
00:02:37,367 --> 00:02:41,267
<i>If Irie learns that I was proposed to</i>
<i>by Kin-chan,</i>

51
00:02:42,067 --> 00:02:45,133
<i>what would he think?</i>

52
00:02:45,733 --> 00:02:47,633
<i>Would Irie</i>

53
00:02:48,133 --> 00:02:51,500
<i>be surprised even a little bit?</i>

54
00:02:52,633 --> 00:02:54,800
<i>Or...</i>

