60
00:05:07,833 --> 00:05:10,100
{\an8}Stop being so formal.

61
00:05:10,267 --> 00:05:12,967
We'll be a family soon.

62
00:05:13,133 --> 00:05:15,267
Let's help out each other.

63
00:05:15,433 --> 00:05:17,500
Thank you so much.

64
00:05:18,433 --> 00:05:22,033
