this year.

69
00:05:32,633 --> 00:05:34,400
Naoki.

70
00:05:35,067 --> 00:05:38,100
You told us that we'd become
a family.

71
00:05:38,533 --> 00:05:41,767
So I don't want to hide anything.

72
00:05:43,733 --> 00:05:44,967
Naoki.

73
00:05:45,567 --> 00:05:47,100
What a guy.

74
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:48,700
Therefore,

75
00:05:48,867 --> 00:05:51,567
I'd like the wedding to be after
the surgery,

76
00:05:51,733 --> 00:05:55,700
next year, if possible.

77
00:05:56,833 --> 00:05:58,233
I see.

78
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,767
It's my precious Sahoko's wedding.

79
00:06:00,933 --> 00:06:03,867
We might need that much time
to prepare.

80
00:06:04,933 --> 00:06:08,600
It's the June bride, isn't it?

81
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:11,267
Then it'll be around this time
next year.

82
00:06:11,433 --> 00:06:13,633
-I see.
-Okay.

83
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,300
Does he still have time?

84
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:21,400
Chairman, your next appointment
is getting close.

85
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:23,567
Oh, all right.

86
00:06:23,733 --> 00:06:25,467
See you then.

87
00:06:34,233 --> 00:06:36,400
It's like a dream

88
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:41,833
