94
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:03,267
-You'd better rest now.
-Yeah.

95
00:07:04,967 --> 00:07:06,733
Naoki.

96
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:09,333
Thank you.

97
00:07:12,733 --> 00:07:14,533
But,

98
00:07:15,433 --> 00:07:18,033
