183
00:12:36,067 --> 00:12:37,867
You're right. Let's go.

184
00:12:38,033 --> 00:12:39,600
-Let's go then.
-Yeah.

185
00:12:41,767 --> 00:12:44,333
Rainbow Bridge looks nice.

186
00:12:46,267 --> 00:12:47,800
What's wrong, Kotoko?

187
00:12:49,467 --> 00:12:51,633
That's Irie.

188
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:53,500
That's okay.

189
00:12:53,667 --> 00:12:56,467
Is the girl next to him his fiancé?

190
00:12:56,633 --> 00:13:01,500
She looks so much like
a high-class girl.

191
00:13:02,633 --> 00:13:05,367
Is this Kotoko?

192
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:11,533
Oh, Sahoko. Nice to see you again.

193
00:13:11,700 --> 00:13:15,233
What a coincidence.
Are you on a date too?

194
00:13:16,733 --> 00:13:19,867
She's my fiancé, Sahoko Oizumi.

195
00:13:20,033 --> 00:13:22,467
How do you do?
I'm Sahoko Oizumi.

196
00:13:22,633 --> 00:13:24,600
Nice to meet you.

197
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:26,200
Nice to meet you.

198
00:13:26,367 --> 00:13:28,367
I'm Kinnosuke Ikezawa.

199
00:13:28,533 --> 00:13:30,700
I'm a cook at Kotoko's dad's
restaurant.

200
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:33,967
Wow, you're the successor
of her father.

201
00:13:34,067 --> 00:13:37,033
No, no. I'm still in training.

202
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:39,167
What made you come here?

203
00:13:40,267 --> 00:13:43,100
Actually, we're going to an art
exhibition in Ginza.

204
00:13:43,267 --> 00:13:46,733
But Naoki suggested to stop by here
before that.

205
00:13:46,900 --> 00:13:49,700
He said that there was
a great place.

206
00:13:49,867 --> 00:13:53,100
You said that you wanted to go
to a place that had an open feel.

207
00:13:54,433 --> 00:13:57,567
<i>This is the place</i>
<i>that he came with me.</i>

208
00:13:57,733 --> 00:14:01,133
<i>He takes Sahoko here.</i>

209
00:14:01,933 --> 00:14:03,500
<i>For Irie,</i>

210
00:14:03,667 --> 00:14:07,300
<i>the first date with me</i>
<i>was nothing.</i>

211
00:14:07,467 --> 00:14:10,200
<i>It was something</i>
<i>that he didn't care about.</i>

212
00:14:10,367 --> 00:14:13,000
Right. If you don't mind it,

213
00:14:13,067 --> 00:14:15,500
