{\an8}The possibility of a person getting
hit by a shooting star

696
00:52:26,633 --> 00:52:28,467
{\an8}is one in ten billion.

697
00:52:30,300 --> 00:52:31,467
{\an8}Meeting you

698
00:52:31,567 --> 00:52:34,100
{\an8}is a miracle even rarer than that.

